ass=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然個個盤可能會有所不同，但我都想闊吓巴打你轉發內容指「2月16-21日會是緩沖期」，即係咩意思？因為我呀爸1月中有做過檢測的，嚟緊聽晚先再做"},{"pid":"6812624cf12e0a31b794123931bfdda730f329fa","tid":2409831,"uid":311436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3104c453ab4cba7dfa357c5806865798aec7291e","tid":2409831,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5bd75704c1b6b57649f6ca2ba3bce630b84d8b","tid":2409831,"uid":311436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d5563205d5983347f6590487f561cde603769c4","tid":2409831,"uid":311436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:20:54.000Z","msg":"我試過最快第2日收到，最遲2日<br />\n<br />\n但係li幾日好爆，可能會耐d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩有師父話尋日中午交樽，岩岩收到短訊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"謝謝巴打詳細解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然個個盤可能會有所不同，但我都想闊吓巴打你轉發內容指「2月16-21日會是緩沖期」，即係咩意思？因為我呀爸1月中有做過檢測的，嚟緊聽晚先再做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T00:07:44.000Z","msg":"即係政府規定22/2必需做過檢測才可進入地盤， 至於22/2 之前就因應大判決定放唔放你入去"},{"pid":"868bb007ccff8ed59445cdff8c98541ea15e62d3","tid":2409831,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6812624cf12e0a31b794123931bfdda730f329fa","tid":2409831,"uid":311436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3104c453ab4cba7dfa357c5806865798aec7291e","tid":2409831,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5bd75704c1b6b57649f6ca2ba3bce630b84d8b","tid":2409831,"uid":311436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩有師父話尋日中午交樽，岩岩收到短訊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"謝謝巴打詳細解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然個個盤可能會有所不同，但我都想闊吓巴打你轉發內容指「2月16-21日會是緩沖期」，即係咩意思？因為我呀爸1月中有做過檢測的，嚟緊聽晚先再做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T00:07:44.000Z","msg":"即係政府規定22/2必需做過檢測才可進入地盤， 至於22/2 之前就因應大判決定放唔放你入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"明白，謝謝巴打<br />\n報告返先，我呀爸17／2下午4點幾去做，18／2朝早7點幾已收到短訊可以趕得切去開工"},{"pid":"367e8b4004f601bf2bbf17bb362126b28f146bee","tid":2409831,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:41:08.000Z","msg":"599J強制檢測途徑：<br />\n（一）於流動採樣站接受檢測服務（名單及服務對象：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=23e3551d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[中資]<br />\n（二）於社區檢測中心接受檢測服務（名單：<a href=\"http://www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.communitytest.gov.hk%2Fzh-HK%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=248f45ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.communitytest.gov.hk/zh-HK/</a>）[中資]<br />\n（三）於121間郵政局、20個港鐵站設置的自動派發機或醫院管理局47間指定普通科門診診所索取深喉唾液測試樣本收集包，並把樣本交回指定樣本收集點（派發點及時間，以及樣本收集點及時間：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fearly-testing.html&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=23e3551d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/chi/early-testing.html</a>）[難確定，或有中資]<br />\n（四）於醫管局普通科門診診所按照醫管局醫護人員的指示接受檢測<br />\n（五）自行安排接受由衞生署認可，並可就檢測結果發出電話短訊通知的私營化驗所提供的檢測（名單：<a href=\"http://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FList_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=0d1b338b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/List_of_recognised_laboratories_RTPCR.pdf</a>）<br />\n（六）使用衞生防護中心派發到相關指明地方的樣本瓶（如適用），並按有關指示交回已採樣本的檢測樣本收集瓶。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><blockquote>鈕祜祿&middot;甄嬛</blockquote><br />\n【2021年】【0217 LIVE】衞生署及醫管局4點半疫情簡報會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aKuzRpV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aKuzRpV</a><br />\n#31 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"}]}